["Castel di Sasso is a comune (municipality) in the Province of Caserta in the Italian region Campania, located about 40 kilometres (25\u00a0mi) north of Naples and about 14 kilometres (9\u00a0mi) northwest of Caserta.","Castel di Sasso borders the following municipalities: Caiazzo, Capua, Liberi, Piana di Monte Verna, Pontelatone.","This Campanian location article is a stub. You can help Wikipedia by expanding it."]